&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen in Endoscopy for a Band 5 staff Nurse. This is a full time position consisting of working hours that currently range from Monday to Saturday, with a view to potential expansion to Sunday working and evenings. You will also need to participate in our on call rota which spans 7 days a week. Flexibility is an essential element to our service provision. Previous experience is not required as in house training will be given. Genuine interest in the specialty would be preferable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our specialty is a very busy one that requires an enthusiastic individual who is eager to learn and develop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cross cover working will be essential covering Cannock Chase Hospital and Wolverhampton.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information and to arrange informal visits, please contact either Senior Sister R.J.Wilson ext. (01902) 694191 at New Cross Hospital, Or Senior Sister N. Thrupp Endoscopy CCH (01543) 576282&lt;/p&gt;
